{"tid":1714121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［為區選抗洗腦］扮工師做多一件事","createTime":"2019-11-12T23:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T01:07:03.000Z","uid":173918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cd492033a6dfa9387c50f52055dc2b9531c086","tid":1714121,"uid":173918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:47:05.000Z","msg":"係地鐵站一人拎一份免費報然後扔落垃圾桶<br />\n每朝都極大量廢老貪免費而睇<br />\n今朝啲免費報仲要大大隻字叫人投共黨<br />\n一人行多一步！"},{"pid":"3e937bd60f19d8b101159f88cbd47a23405f1361","tid":1714121,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:47:51.000Z","msg":"有做緊啦"},{"pid":"4f997608b68407e727300701e0c73bfcd5667924","tid":1714121,"uid":278228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:49:09.000Z","msg":"借po一個位<br />\n大家好，示威其實都4個月<br />\n我地每次行動都會影響到民生，<br />\n琴日我係沙田去暴大，<br />\n沿途好多街彷屌road block，又話過分乜乜77<br />\n但冇人提過黑警好似殺人咁攻中大<br />\n因為呢件事<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔關佢事</span></strong></span><br />\n每次咁辛苦做咁多野，到頭嚟都係要比人屌<br />\n既然係咁，<br />\n大家係咪時候諗下要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直搗皇龍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔關政見問題，係有的確為所不少既人只關注生計<br />\n同有冇屋企番，甚至會主動清road block<br />\n即使唔係撐警<br />\n既然守中大又要送頭，守旺角又要通頂<br />\n但係都迫唔到政府做啲乜<br />\n<br />\n4個月喇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解宜家仲唔升級去搞啲官</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n至少仲會多人支持"},{"pid":"06ab7c9c819321f4e0caa719ac35b4f5891a756a","tid":1714121,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:49:10.000Z","msg":"其實我地有冇資源學大公 文匯咁派免費報"},{"pid":"a0f0e028cbcc673e73baecd4cd76b33efaa45740","tid":1714121,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:31:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbcac2f12204172ddfd5e6130b80006d19660e91","tid":1714121,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e937bd60f19d8b101159f88cbd47a23405f1361","tid":1714121,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:47:51.000Z","msg":"有做緊啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:07:03.000Z","msg":"至少三份喇"}]}